ized by MAJU \ntalked by Prof Dr. Ameena Zehra, Department of Psychology, University of Karachi \n \n \n \n \n \n \n     Held on March 22nd, 2019, MAJU Karachi \nP a g e  | 6 \n \n4. Quality Design in Business Management Program (QDBMP) \nAttended one day Workshop on Designing Quality in Business Management Programs and Embedding Future \nSkills in the Program’s Strategic Plan organized by QEC of the Institute of Business Management, Karachi \n \n \n \n \n \n \n     Held on Oct 18th, 2018, IoBM, Karachi \n \n \n5. Executive Breakfast (CELDD) \nAttended a Workshop on Four Decades of Real Estate in Karachi (1980 to 2018) organized by Mohammad Ali \nJinnah University CELDD, Karachi \n \n \n \n \n \n \n     Held on Aug 31st, 2018, MAJU, Karachi \n \n6. E-Learning Capacity Building Workshop (MOODLE) \nAttended a Workshop on E-Learning Capacity Building Workshop: Be a Competitive Teacher with the help of \nMOODLE organized by Mohammad Ali Jinnah QEC, Karachi \n \n \n \n \n \n \n     Held on May 17th, 2018, at MAJU, Karachi \n \n7. 2nd NRCMB at SZABIST \nOrganized the 2nd National Research Conference on Management and Business (NRCMB) on the theme of Building \nBridges between Industry and Academia  \n \n                                                   Held on November 24-25, 2017 at SZABIST 90, Karachi \n \n8. 2nd International CPEC Business and Research Conference (ICPEC-BRC2) \nAttended the 2-days conference on China-Pakistan Economic Corridor – An Opportunity for Economics and Social \nTransformation organized by IBA Karachi in partnership with SILC Business School, Shanghai University, China \n \n \n \n \n \n \n     Held on March 15th and 16th, 2017, IBA, Karachi  \n \n9. 14th International Conference on Statistical Sciences (ICSS-14) \nAttended ICSS 14 at Jinnah Sindh Medical University Karachi organized by ISOSS and presented 3 research papers  \n       Held on March 2016, JSMU, Karachi  \n \n10. 12th International Conference on Statistical Sciences (ICSS-12) \nAt